<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0218001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218001"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0218002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218002">阿羅毘（Aḷavi）生之比丘尼。</note>
<note n="0218003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218003">出離（nissaraṇa）者，此指涅槃。</note>
<note n="0219004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219004">道足（pada）導向涅槃足與涅槃之道足。</note>
<note n="0219005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219005">khandhāsaṁ adhikuṭṭanā = khandhā tesaṁ adhikuṭṭana-gaṇḍikā。</note>
<note n="0219006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219006">雜阿含經卷四五．二（大正藏二．三二六a）。</note>
<note n="0219007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219007">日住者，指日中飯後入禪之謂。</note>
<note n="0219008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219008">二指之智慧者，佛音解釋為婦人以二指取線，而予割斷。《長老尼偈》之註者解釋為：婦女自幼小即看顧於米，以二指探試米之熟與未熟。</note>
<note n="0220009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0220009">雜阿含經卷四五．三（大正藏二．三二六b）。</note>
<note n="0221010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0221010">雜阿含經卷四五．七（大正藏二．三二七c）。</note>
<note n="0222011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0222011">八種之世間得達。今則心不為彼等所執，而謂之解脫。</note>
<note n="0222012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0222012">雜阿含經卷四五．四（大正藏二．三二六c）。</note>
<note n="0223013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0223013"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0223014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0223014">此句之前，尚有 idhāgatā tādisikā bhaveyyuṁ 一句，應將混入其次之《蓮華色偈》之第二句。然註釋者許此句，而解釋為：「如汝來此之不具知己或友誼，而彼等亦然。」今如可除去。</note>
<note n="0223015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0223015">依漢譯，此作為惡魔之偈。</note>
<note n="0224016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0224016">雜阿含經卷四五．八（大正藏二．三二八a）。</note>
<note n="0224017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0224017"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0224018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0224018"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0225019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0225019">雜阿含經卷四五．九（大正藏二．三二八b）。</note>
<note n="0226020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226020">雜阿含經卷四五．一〇（大正藏二．三二八c）。</note>
<note n="0226021" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226021">教見 pāsaṇḍa 一語，出自 pāsa 係蹄之語。此義即人類心中懷有異學異見之係蹄，指佛教以外之異見。</note>
<note n="0227022" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0227022">雜阿含經卷四五．六（大正藏二．三二七b）。</note>
<note n="0228023" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0228023">雜阿含經卷四五．五（大正藏二．三二七a）。</note>
</p>
